snippet.title: FNAF World: Outplay - Announcement trailer
snippet.description:
The announcement trailer is up! Yes, that's right. I'm making a new game. It will be a short game, which is a recreation of FNAF WORLD from an RPG to a platformer. So expect further information from me here, on Twitter, or on the Gamejolt game page!

Twitter: https://twitter.com/Rextair
Gamejolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/fnafworldoutplay/749299
